{"tid":293468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（香港要效法）特朗普：新移民至少五年不得享有美國福利","createTime":"2017-06-22T07:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T08:21:05.000Z","uid":41351,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"811676101f07edd986cef7a033cb4c9880685798","tid":293468,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　新浪美股訊 北京時間22日彭博報導，&ldquo;我認為現在是推出新移民規則的時候了，也就是說，那些要求入籍我們國家的人必須有足夠的經濟來源維持個人生活，而且至少五年內不能享受美國的福利。&rdquo;美國總統特朗普在愛荷華州Cedar Rapids舉行的一場集會上表示。<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;我們很快會提出相關的立法。&rdquo; 特朗普表示，來美國的人&ldquo;必須認同我們的價值觀，愛我們的人民&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n　　特朗普稱，&ldquo;我們也希望保留針對處境艱難而真正需要幫助的美國人的社會福利。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　註：1996年福利改革後，多類合法移民五年內不得享有大部分聯邦福利。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20170622/2/70/2/特朗普提議新移民至少五年不得享有美國福利-7589025.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170622%2F2%2F70%2F2%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8F%90%E8%AD%B0%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9-7589025.html&d=TqiXZQoAFblHPQJEzl5ZAFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=a25e99bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20170622/2/70/2/特朗普提議新移民至少五年不得享有美國福利-7589025.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/154634_d5fae525239806c7090ab88622ed232c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F154634_d5fae525239806c7090ab88622ed232c.jpg&h=37eebd4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e6e30b034534351ca2dbe3867815f7f934a1f97","tid":293468,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等睇支狗難民加搵食左膠：不人道！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass